item.title: AutoKaggle: A Multi-Agent Framework for Autonomous Data Science Competitions
item.description: AutoKaggle, a novel multi-agent framework, automates Kaggle data science competitions with high accuracy, integrating LLM reasoning, iterative debugging, and a custom machine learning tools library.
